== 额外信息 ==
*该剧的背景是[[中国南方航空公司|中国南方航空公司]]<ref name="fish ">{{cite web |url=http://et.21cn.com/tv/roll/a/2013/0514/17/21640737.shtml |title=《云上的诱惑》收官 非黄档播出获关注 |accessdate=2013 |publisher=21CN |work= |language=zh-cn |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219143349/http://et.21cn.com/tv/roll/a/2013/0514/17/21640737.shtml |archive-date=2013-12-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

*该剧是中国首部[[航空|航空]]题材电视剧<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sd.xinhuanet.com/news/2013-05/05/c_115643247.htm|title=行业剧为荧屏周播探路 "云上的诱惑"看点十足|accessdate=2013|publisher=新华网|work=|language=zh-cn|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120627/http://www.sd.xinhuanet.com/news/2013-05/05/c_115643247.htm|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>。

